; CNAME include fragment used by example.com_include.fwd to exercise the BIND
; $INCLUDE compatibility layer. Owners are relative to the including zone's
; origin (include-test.example.); targets use RFC 6761 reserved domains.
alias  IN  CNAME  www.example.com.
mail   IN  CNAME  mx.example.org.
help   IN  CNAME  support.example.net.
